
# Linux Commands
- whoami
- uname -a 
		-  get os details
- clear or press ctl + l
	- clear console

- sudo bash
	- go to root user
- su abi
	- go to user

- Create a new user and pwd
	- sudo useradd daffy
 	- sudo passwd daffy

 - Create a file 
	- sudo vi  text.txt
	press i to insert

- verbose mode
- 	

chown 777 text.txt -> giving permission 777
